chage -l kevin // is used to see the values for kevin user

usermod -c test1 kevin //  to put comment as test1

usermod -e 2020/12/23 kevin  // -e is for expiry

How to see the id of kevin?
id kevin

change primary group of kevin?
usermod -g LPU kevin

how to add supplementary group ?
usermod -aG LPU2 kevin  // -a append .no info loss 

options :
-L to lock 
-l to change the username 
-U to unblock the password
-c to comment
-e to set expiry date
-u to change uid
-g to change gid
  






